# Block AMP URLs with 410 Gone status to prevent Google Search Console warnings
# These rules prevent Google from crawling guessed AMP URLs on static sites

# Block /amp path
/amp    /amp    410

# Block any path ending with /amp
/*/amp    /*/amp    410

# Block query parameter ?amp
/?amp    /?amp    410

# Block query parameter ?amp= followed by anything
/?amp=*    /?amp=*    410
